snippet.title: Road Rash gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Road Rash, PC game produced by Electronic Arts in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/road-rash/1999/
Running fast and furious a couple of arcade stages. The first one the police caught me... the second was a better race!
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Fatal Racing - https://youtu.be/V--QhwtC89I
Skyroads X-mas Edition - https://youtu.be/Sc2BJ9bwM80
Race Mania - https://youtu.be/rliN6ljOTiQ
